dct_description_sm: Title supplied by cataloger. Wall maps. Each map is cloth backed and mounted on wooden rods in a scroll. Each sheet individually numbered. Library has: [1]. Prooptiko schediagramma tēs Mesaiōnikēs Kōnstantinoupalēs; [2]. Valkanikoi Polemoi 1912-1913; [3]. Hellada kai Mikra Asia 1918-1922; 9. Hē Eurōpē kata to 565 m. Ch.; 10. Ho Christianikes kai Mōamethanikos Kosmos. No. [1] dated: 17-11-76. Nos. [2]-[3] belong to series: Historikoi chartes Loukopoulou; nos. 9-10 belong to series: Historikoi chartes D. Dēmētrakou-P. Karolidou.
